any of these events, nor about any of these
people. Why? -- Because if she had been
there, she would not have had much interest
in anything like that. She'd have found a
nice quiet corner, and written a poem about
her cat.

When you are a Strat, you are committed
to complete ignorance about everything.
You have all the intelligence and knowledge
of a lump of rock. When you are a quasi-
Strat, you claim to be human, but you insist
on behaving and 'thinking' as though you
were a lump of rock.

